data.message: I want eminem ones really badly 😭.I have always been an eminem fan.I am 14 and a half.Eminem was there for me when I couldn't talk to anybody about my problems.I relate to how he feels on certain subjects on life.I already have some merch like two cds,a shirt from the song berzerk,and The newest poster.I would love to have these shoes for myself because I never win anything big like this and I have been going through things lately.I would die to see eminem but could settle for the next best thing.I have been a fan and always will be.I know most of the lyrics to his songs and the one I relate to most is when I'm gone (towards my father).I also trained myself to rap to his songs like rap god and back to the basics like lose yourself and slim shady.
